<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2013-07-31</DATELINE><TITLE>A patient with severe respiratory failure caused by novel human coronavirus</TITLE><BODY>We report a case of a 45-year-old patient who developed severe acute respiratory distress syndrome accompanied by renal failure. An infection with a novel human coronavirus was confirmed and found to be the reason for rapidly progressive respiratory failure of our patient.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>